keyInterpolateWithFormatting: replace this {{value, number}} (only number is supported)
keyContext_male: the male variant (is parsed as normal key and context is ignored)
keyContext_female: the female variant (is parsed as normal key and context is ignored)
keyPluralSimple_one: the singular (is parsed as plural under one key - keyPluralSimple)
keyPluralSimple_other: the plural (is parsed as plural under one key - keyPluralSimple)
